OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry
OL,6,Fevening with hazy sunny spells, but
OL,7,Fcloudier around the Moray Firth.
OL,8,FRemaining dry for the rest of the
OL,9,Fnight, the best of the clear spells in
OL,10,Fthe west where it may become quite
OL,11,Fcool.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FA dry, bright and warm day.
OL,14,FEarly cloud in the east will gradually
OL,15,Fclear, leaving good sunny spells for
OL,16,Fthe rest of the day.
OL,17,
OL,18,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry
OL,19,Fand very warm on Thursday with sunny
OL,20,Fspells. Cloudier, cooler on Friday and
OL,21,FSaturday with outbreaks of rain
